# install port audio and then:
gcc -o octaveless octaveless.c -lportaudio && ./octaveless

# Type A b B C d D e E F g G a A b B ... and listen to the sound go around
# Ctrl+C to quit

# only tested on Mac OS 10.6, but should work anywhere portaudio does

Example sounds:

  http://www.jefftk.com/octaveless/A.mp3
  http://www.jefftk.com/octaveless/Bb.mp3
